Global 2-Hydroxy-4-n-octoxy Benzophenone Market Insights
2-Hydroxy-4-n-octoxy Benzophenone Market size was valued at USD 0.12 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.21 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.2% from 2024 to 2030.

2-Hydroxy-4-n-octoxy Benzophenone Market Overview
The global market for 2-Hydroxy-4-n-octoxy Benzophenone is experiencing robust growth due to its increasing demand in the manufacturing of UV absorbers and stabilizers for various applications, including coatings, plastics, and personal care products. As of 2025, the market size is valued at approximately USD 200 million, with expectations for continuous expansion driven by rising awareness of the importance of UV protection in different sectors. The compound's superior ability to absorb ultraviolet radiation and enhance product longevity makes it highly desirable for use in industries where UV exposure is a significant concern.

As the demand for personal care and cosmetic products continues to rise, the market for 2-Hydroxy-4-n-octoxy Benzophenone is also expected to see growth in the skincare segment, primarily due to its ability to prevent UV-induced damage to the skin. The market is forecasted to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.5% from 2025 to 2030, with the Asia Pacific region leading the market share, followed by North America and Europe.

